//[Reference] 'It feels good to patrol the village every day.'
staxel.village.dialogue.job.Sweeper.line:10000100=每天都巡视村子的感觉不错.
//[Reference] 'I'm the one keeping our streets clean!'
staxel.village.dialogue.job.Sweeper.line:10000200=我是让街道保持整洁的人!
//[Reference] 'It's becoming harder and harder to find a place to store my ^c:d03e37;brooms^c:pop;.'
staxel.village.dialogue.job.Sweeper.line:10000300=找一个地方存放我的 ^c:d03e37;brooms^c:pop;.越来越难了.
//[Reference] 'I think I'm going to have to install a few more racks...'
staxel.village.dialogue.job.Sweeper.line:10000400=我想我得再装几个架子...
//[Reference] 'What I wouldn't give for an Arcus 2001...'
staxel.village.dialogue.job.Sweeper.line:10000500=我可没办法给你一把Arcus 2001...
//[Reference] 'The sweeping action is said to be divine.'
staxel.village.dialogue.job.Sweeper.line:10000600=扫地可是一件神圣的事情.
//[Reference] 'I hear nothing can clean a street even half as well.'
staxel.village.dialogue.job.Sweeper.line:10000700=我听说没有什么东西能把街道打扫干净.
//[Reference] 'Someone keeps vandalising the town hall's signboard...'
staxel.village.dialogue.job.Sweeper.line:10000800=经常有人蓄意破坏市镇厅的牌子...
//[Reference] 'They plaster it with posters of infuriatingly adorable kittens.'
staxel.village.dialogue.job.Sweeper.line:10000900=他们会贴上一只可爱的小猫做出生气表情样子的海报.
//[Reference] 'I'll bet my broom that it's ^c:1486b0;{0-tomboy_name}^c:pop;.'
staxel.village.dialogue.job.Sweeper.line:10001000=我拿我的扫帚打赌是 ^c:1486b0;{0-tomboy_name}^c:pop;做的.
//[Reference] 'Someday I'll get myself an auto-cleaner.'
staxel.village.dialogue.job.Sweeper.line:10001100=总有一天我会给自己买一辆垃圾车.
//[Reference] 'It wouldn't be anywhere near as effective as I am...'
staxel.village.dialogue.job.Sweeper.line:10001200=它不会像我一样有效率...
//[Reference] 'But at least it would decrease my workload.'
staxel.village.dialogue.job.Sweeper.line:10001300=但至少它可以减轻我的工作压力.
//[Reference] 'Maybe I could convince ^c:1486b0;{0-scientist_name}^c:pop; to build me one?'
staxel.village.dialogue.job.Sweeper.line:10001400=或许我应该去说服 ^c:1486b0;{0-scientist_name}^c:pop; 帮我造一个?
//[Reference] 'Feel free to give me a hand whenever you're free.'
staxel.village.dialogue.job.Sweeper.line:10001500=如果又空的话你可以帮帮忙.
//[Reference] 'Pick up a ^c:d03e37;broom^c:pop; and you can use it to push dropped items around!'
staxel.village.dialogue.job.Sweeper.line:10001600=拿起那个 ^c:d03e37;扫帚^c:pop; 这样你就可以把丢在地上的东西扫走了!
//[Reference] 'It's an effective way to clean up any mess you make!'
staxel.village.dialogue.job.Sweeper.line:10001700=这是清理你制造出来的垃圾的好方法.
//[Reference] '^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;, just a word of warning.'
staxel.village.dialogue.job.Sweeper.line:10001800=^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;, 只是提醒你一句.
//[Reference] 'Please keep your animals out of the ^c:1486b0;village square^c:pop;.'
staxel.village.dialogue.job.Sweeper.line:10001900=请别让你的宠物来 ^c:1486b0;小镇广场^c:pop;
//[Reference] 'I have no interest in cleaning up after them.'
staxel.village.dialogue.job.Sweeper.line:10002000=我可不想跟在它们身后打扫.
//[Reference] 'Sometimes I'm overcome by an inexorable need to sweep a chimney.'
staxel.village.dialogue.job.Sweeper.line:10002100=有时候我会突然非常渴望去把烟囱清理一下.
//[Reference] 'Unfortunately, we don't have many chimneys around here...'
staxel.village.dialogue.job.Sweeper.line:10002200=不幸的是这儿可没有烟囱...
